title: You wont want to miss this! Pending in Seattle. 2 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: Mid-century charmer right by Lake Washington!
Come bask in the sun drenched living room while enjoying the comfort of the newly installed air conditioning!
Once the weather starts cooling off, cozy up to the wood burning fireplace either in the living room or in the downstairs rec room.

The home also features a spacious, light and bright kitchen with an island and eating space that opens to an expansive and luxurious deck where you can bbq and watch the dogs run around in the large, fenced backyard.
Both generous sized bedrooms are on the main level and the primary bedroom has a 3/4 bathroom en suite.
Downstairs you'll find a spacious rec room with fireplace and a utility/laundry room ready for your ideas and final touches.
